<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="da">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TrendAgent ETF Monthly — Uge {{ week_number }}</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f6f9; color: #2c3e50; font-size: 14px; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f2027 0%, #203a43 50%, #2c5364 100%); color: white; padding: 20px 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
    .header h1 { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
    .header h1 span { color: #4ecdc4; }
    .header-meta { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; margin-top: 4px; }
    .badge { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: right; }
    .badge .val { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 800; }
    .badge .lbl { font-size: 10px; color: #aaa; }
    .container { max-width: 1300px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }

    /* ALERTS */
    .alert-box { border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .alert-trail { background: #fef3cd; border-left: 4px solid #f59c00; }
    .alert-title { font-weight: 700; font-size: 13px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .alert-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; padding: 5px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06); font-size: 12px; }
    .alert-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .tag-red { background: #d93025; color: white; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }

    /* SIGNALER */
    .signal-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .signal-box { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 16px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .signal-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .signal-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5; font-size: 12px; }
    .signal-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .tag-sell { background: #fce8e6; color: #d93025; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
    .tag-buy { background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e8e3e; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }

    /* BENCHMARK */
    .benchmark-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .bench-card { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .bench-val { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; margin: 8px 0; }
    .bench-lbl { font-size: 11px; color: #888; }

    /* AKTIVE POSITIONER */
    .section-card { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 18px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .section-title { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 14px; color: #1a1a2e; }
    table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
    th { background: #f0f4f8; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; color: #555; font-size: 11px; }
    td { padding: 8px 10px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5; vertical-align: middle; }
    tr:hover { background: #fafafa; }
    .rank-badge { background: #1a1a2e; color: white; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; }
    .trend-acc { color: #1e8e3e; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; }
    .trend-slow { color: #f59c00; font-weight: 600; font-size: 12px; }
    .trend-side { color: #888; font-size: 12px; }
    .mom-fast { background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e8e3e; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
    .mom-stable { background: #e8f4fd; color: #1565c0; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; }
    .mom-slow { background: #fff3e0; color: #e65100; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; }
    .mom-flat { background: #fce8e6; color: #d93025; padding: 2px 7px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; }
    .shift-bull { background: #e6f4ea; color: #1e8e3e; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 6px; }
    .shift-bear { background: #fce8e6; color: #d93025; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; margin-left: 6px; }
    .category-tag { background: #e8f4fd; color: #1565c0; padding: 1px 6px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 10px; }
    .pos { color: #1e8e3e; font-weight: 700; }
    .neg { color: #d93025; font-weight: 700; }

    /* MARKEDSMULIGHEDER */
    .opp-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(220px, 1fr)); gap: 10px; }
    .opp-card { background: #f8fbff; border: 1px solid #e0eaf5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 12px; }
    .opp-rank { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: #1565c0; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .opp-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 12px; color: #1a1a2e; margin-bottom: 2px; }
    .opp-ticker { font-size: 10px; color: #888; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .opp-stats { display: flex; gap: 10px; font-size: 11px; }
    .opp-stat { color: #555; }
    .opp-stat span { font-weight: 700; color: #1e8e3e; }

    /* HISTORIK */
    .sold-table td { color: #888; }

    /* METODIK */
    .metodik { background: white; border-radius: 10px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .metodik h3 { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1a1a2e; border-bottom: 2px solid #4ecdc4; padding-bottom: 6px; }
    .metodik-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; }
    .metodik-col h4 { font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: #4ecdc4; margin: 10px 0 6px; }
    .metodik-col p, .metodik-col li { font-size: 11px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .metodik-col ul { padding-left: 16px; }
    .disclaimer { background: #f0f7ff; border-left: 3px solid #4ecdc4; padding: 10px 14px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 11px; color: #555; margin-top: 12px; font-style: italic; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HEADER -->
<div class="header">
  <div>
    <h1>📡 TrendAgent <span>ETF Monthly</span></h1>
    <div class="header-meta">Strategisk status opdateret {{ timestamp }} (Uge {{ week_number }})</div>
  </div>
  <div class="badge">
    <div class="lbl">BENCHMARK: {{ benchmark_name }} ({{ '%+.2f'|format(benchmark_return) }}% sidste md.)</div>
    <div class="val" style="color: {{ '#4ecdc4' if diff_to_benchmark >= 0 else '#ff6b6b' }}">
      {{ '%+.2f'|format(diff_to_benchmark) }}% alpha
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">

  <!-- TRAIL STOP -->
  {% if trail_stop_alerts %}
  <div class="alert-box alert-trail">
    <div class="alert-title">⚠️ Trail Stop — {{ trail_stop_alerts|length }} fond(e) udløst (tærskel: {{ trail_stop_pct }}%)</div>
    {% for a in trail_stop_alerts %}
    <div class="alert-row">
      <span><strong>{{ a.name }}</strong></span>
      <span>
        HWM: {{ a.hwm }} &nbsp;|&nbsp; Nu: {{ a.curr }} &nbsp;
        <span class="tag-red">{{ '%+.1f'|format(a.fall_pct) }}% fra top</span>
        &nbsp; Total: {{ '%+.1f'|format(a.total_ret) }}%
      </span>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- HANDLINGSSIGNALER -->
  {% if sell_signals or buy_signals %}
  <div class="signal-grid">
    <div class="signal-box">
      <div class="signal-title">🔴 Overvej salg / rotation</div>
      {% if sell_signals %}
        {% for f in sell_signals %}
        <div class="signal-item">
          <span class="tag-sell">OUTPERFORMED</span>
          <span>{{ f.name[:40] }} ligger udenfor top 10 (Rank #{{ f.rank }}). Opportunity cost er høj.</span>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
        <div class="signal-item" style="color:#888; font-size:12px;">
          ✅ Ingen salgssignaler — alle aktive positioner holder trit med markedet.
        </div>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% if buy_signals %}
    <div class="signal-box">
      <div class="signal-title">🟢 Rotationsmuligheder</div>
      {% for o in buy_signals %}
      <div class="signal-item">
        <span class="tag-buy">ROTATIONSMÅL</span>
        <span>{{ o.name[:40] }} (Rank #{{ o.rank }}) med 1M afkast på {{ '%+.1f'|format(o.return_1m) }}%</span>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- BENCHMARK -->
  <div class="benchmark-grid">
    <div class="bench-card">
      <div class="bench-lbl">DIN PORTEFØLJE (TOTAL SNIT)</div>
      <div class="bench-val" style="color: {{ '#1e8e3e' if avg_portfolio_return >= 0 else '#d93025' }}">
        {{ '%+.2f'|format(avg_portfolio_return) }}%
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bench-card">
      <div class="bench-lbl">VS. BENCHMARK — {{ benchmark_name }}</div>
      <div class="bench-val" style="color: {{ '#1e8e3e' if diff_to_benchmark >= 0 else '#d93025' }}">
        {{ '%+.2f'|format(diff_to_benchmark) }}%
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- AKTIVE POSITIONER -->
  {% if active_funds %}
  <div class="section-card">
    <div class="section-title">⭐ Aktive Positioner & Relativ Styrke</div>
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>Rank</th>
          <th>Fond</th>
          <th>Trend Velocity</th>
          <th>Momentum Status</th>
          <th>Sidste 1M %</th>
          <th>ÅTD %</th>
          <th>Total Afkast %</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for f in active_funds %}
        <tr>
          <td><span class="rank-badge">#{{ f.rank }}</span></td>
          <td>
            <strong>{{ f.name }}</strong>
            {% if f.trend_shift %}
              <span class="{{ 'shift-bull' if 'BEAR→BULL' in f.trend_shift else 'shift-bear' }}">{{ f.trend_shift }}</span>
            {% endif %}
            <br>
            <small style="color:#888;">{{ f.ticker }}</small>
            <span class="category-tag" style="margin-left:4px;">{{ f.category.split('—')[-1].strip()[:15] if f.category else '' }}</span>
          </td>
          <td class="{{ 'trend-acc' if 'Accelererer' in f.trend_label else 'trend-slow' if 'Bremser' in f.trend_label else 'trend-side' }}">
            {{ f.trend_label }}
          </td>
          <td><span class="{{ f.momentum_class | replace('momentum-', 'mom-') }}">{{ f.momentum_label }}</span></td>
          <td class="{{ 'pos' if (f.return_1m or 0) >= 0 else 'neg' }}">
            {{ '%+.2f'|format(f.return_1m) if f.return_1m is not none else '—' }}%
          </td>
          <td class="{{ 'pos' if (f.return_ytd or 0) >= 0 else 'neg' }}">
            {{ '%+.2f'|format(f.return_ytd) if f.return_ytd is not none else '—' }}%
          </td>
          <td class="{{ 'pos' if f.total_return >= 0 else 'neg' }}" style="font-weight:700;">
            {{ '%+.2f'|format(f.total_return) }}%
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- MARKEDSMULIGHEDER -->
  {% if market_opps %}
  <div class="section-card">
    <div class="section-title">🔭 Top {{ market_opps|length }} Markedsmuligheder (Hele ETF-universet)</div>
    <div class="opp-grid">
      {% for o in market_opps %}
      <div class="opp-card">
        <div class="opp-rank">Rank #{{ o.rank }} af {{ total_count }}</div>
        <div class="opp-name">{{ o.name[:40] }}</div>
        <div class="opp-ticker">{{ o.ticker }}
          {% if o.category %}<span class="category-tag" style="margin-left:4px;">{{ o.category.split('—')[-1].strip()[:12] }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="opp-stats">
          <div class="opp-stat">1M: <span>{{ '%+.1f'|format(o.return_1m) }}%</span></div>
          {% if o.return_ytd %}<div class="opp-stat">ÅTD: <span>{{ '%+.1f'|format(o.return_ytd) }}%</span></div>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div style="font-size:11px; color:#888; margin-top:4px;">{{ o.trend_label }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- SOLGTE POSITIONER -->
  {% if sold_funds %}
  <div class="section-card">
    <div class="section-title">📁 Historik — Solgte Positioner</div>
    <table class="sold-table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Fond</th><th>Købt</th><th>Solgt</th><th>Afkast v. salg</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {% for f in sold_funds %}
        <tr>
          <td>{{ f.name }}<br><small>{{ f.ticker }}</small></td>
          <td>{{ f.buy_date }}</td>
          <td>{{ f.sell_date }}</td>
          <td class="{{ 'pos' if (f.sell_price or 0) > (f.buy_price or 0) else 'neg' }}">
            {% if f.buy_price and f.sell_price %}
              {{ '%+.2f'|format(((f.sell_price - f.buy_price) / f.buy_price * 100)) }}%
            {% else %}—{% endif %}
          </td>
        </tr>
        {% endfor %}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
  {% endif %}

  <!-- METODIK -->
  <div class="metodik">
    <h3>📖 Detaljeret Metodik & Definitioner</h3>
    <div class="metodik-grid">
      <div class="metodik-col">
        <h4>📊 MARKEDSRANK (RELATIV STYRKE)</h4>
        <p>Alle ETF'er i universet rangeres efter 1M afkast. Rank #1 = stærkest momentum. Bruges til at vurdere om dine positioner holder trit med markedet.</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Top Performer:</strong> Top 5 med positivt afkast</li>
          <li><strong>Stabil:</strong> Top 7</li>
          <li><strong>Slower:</strong> Udenfor top 7 eller negativt afkast</li>
          <li><strong>Outperformed:</strong> Udenfor top 10 — andre løber hurtigere</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>📈 TREND VELOCITY</h4>
        <p>Sammenligner ugens afkast mod månedens gennemsnit per uge (1M afkast / 4):</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>🚀 Accelererer:</strong> Ugen er stærkere end månedssnittet</li>
          <li><strong>📉 Bremser:</strong> Ugen er svagere end månedssnittet</li>
          <li><strong>➡️ Stabil:</strong> På linje med månedssnittet</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>🔄 TREND SHIFT</h4>
        <p>Viser om en fond har skiftet trend siden forrige månedlige rapport:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong style="color:#d93025;">BULL→BEAR:</strong> Faldet under MA — overvej rotation</li>
          <li><strong style="color:#1e8e3e;">BEAR→BULL:</strong> Steget over MA — potentielt signal</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="metodik-col">
        <h4>⚠️ TRAIL STOP (HIGH WATER MARK)</h4>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>High Water Mark:</strong> Højeste kurs siden køb — opdateres automatisk</li>
          <li><strong>Fald fra top:</strong> (kurs / HWM − 1) × 100</li>
          <li><strong>Tærskel:</strong> {{ trail_stop_pct }}% — advarsel sendes ved større fald</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>📡 BENCHMARK</h4>
        <p>{{ benchmark_name }} bruges som proxy-benchmark for ETF-universet. Alpha = din porteføljes snit minus benchmark. Positivt alpha = du slår markedet.</p>

        <h4>🔭 MARKEDSMULIGHEDER</h4>
        <p>Top 5 ikke-ejede ETF'er fra universet sorteret efter 1M afkast. Bruges til at identificere potentielle rotationsmål.</p>

        <div class="disclaimer">
          Vi følger momentum og relativ styrke. Vi køber ETF'er der er stærkere end deres historiske gennemsnit og overvejer at rotere ud af ETF'er der mister momentum. Systemet giver signaler — du tager beslutningerne.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
